            "id": "4542823",
            "title": "Hope Bancorp Non-GAAP EPS of $0.27 beats by $0.01, revenue of $145.8M beats by $2.9M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Hope Bancorp <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20376947-hope-bancorp-reports-financial-results-for-the-fourth-quarter-and-full-year-ended-december-31\">press release</a>  (HOPE): Q4  Non-GAAP EPS of $0.27 <font color=\"green\"> beats by $0.01</font>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $145.8M (+23.5% Y/Y) <font color=\"green\"> beats by $2.9M</font>.</li>\n<li>Net interest margin for the fourth quarter of 2025 increased by 1 basis point to 2.90%, up from 2.89% for the third quarter of 2025, and expanded 40 basis points year-over-year, up from 2.50% for the fourth quarter of 2024.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
